room_title: Escape room "Prison Break" by Riddle Escape Room in Phoenix
room_address: 2334 N Scottsdale Rd a120 Scottsdale, AZ 85257
room_description: You wake up one morning locked in a prison cell convicted for a crime that you didn't do. The guards left for their break. Now is your chance to escape! Start cracking codes, finding clues and figure out the only way to escape. You have to hurry: guards will be back in one hour.
